<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Pedido Finalizado</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f9c6b2 0%, #f7b7c0 50%, #bfaee0 100%);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .finalizado-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(191, 174, 224, 0.12);
      background: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .btn-whatsapp {
      background: #25d366;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .btn-whatsapp:hover {
      background: #128c7e;
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light"
    style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f9c6b2 0%, #f7b7c0 50%, #bfaee0 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(191,174,224,0.10);">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center" href="/"
        style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.7rem; letter-spacing:2px; color:#a68bc7;">
        <i class="bi bi-gem me-2" style="font-size:2rem; color:#a68bc7;"></i>
        Joias Elegance
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="finalizado-card">
      <h2 class="mb-3" style="color:#a68bc7;">Pedido Finalizado!</h2>
      <p class="fs-5">Seu pedido foi registrado com sucesso.<br>
        Clique no bot√£o abaixo para enviar os detalhes do pedido pelo WhatsApp:</p>
      <a href="<%= urlWhatsapp %>" target="_blank" class="btn btn-whatsapp">
        <i class="bi bi-whatsapp"></i> Enviar pelo WhatsApp
      </a>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/meus-pedidos" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Ver meus pedidos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>